&lt;p>A raw mango on the branch of a tree &lt;br>
is good for some purposes and bad for others.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A ripe mango on the branch of a tree &lt;br>
is good for some purposes and bad for others.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A parrot cuts the mango using his beak and leaves the mango on the branch. &lt;br>
That mango is good for some purposes and bad for others.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>